videos.description: Udoka Azubuike maneuvers around the paint to find the open throw down.
videos.headline: Azubuike slams one home

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike muscles through the paint for another two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Azubuike throws down again

videos.description: Malik Newman drives the baseline and finishes with a huge one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Newman throws down one-handed jam

videos.description: Devonte' Graham drives coast-to-coast and dishes to Mitch Lightfoot in the paint for the slam.
videos.headline: Graham dishes to Lightfoot for huge throwdown

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk gets the ball in the corner and pump-fakes Jacob Young followed by a drained 3.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk sends Young flying off the court with pump fake

videos.description: Kerwin Roche II intercepts the inbounds pass and carries it down the court for the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Roche's huge steal leads to and-1

videos.description: Devonte' Graham tosses it up to Mitch Lightfoot on the fast break and he throws it down to seal the victory over Texas.
videos.headline: Graham-Lightfoot connection sends Kansas off with a bang
